          <div class='step s25'><div class='name'>25%</div></div>
          <div class='step s50'><div class='name'>50%</div></div>
          <div class='step s75'><div class='name'>75%</div></div>
          <div class='step s100'><div class='name'>100%</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class='slidervalue hidden' data-slider-type='percent'>0%</div>   
        <div>Rural</div>
        <div class='slider' data-slider-name='d_hou_rur' data-slider-options='{"range":"min","value":25,"step":25,"animate":"true"}'>
          <div class='step s0'><div class='name'>0%</div></div>
          <div class='step s25'><div class='name'>25%</div></div>
          <div class='step s50'><div class='name'>50%</div></div>
          <div class='step s75'><div class='name'>75%</div></div>
          <div class='step s100'><div class='name'>100%</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class='slidervalue hidden' data-slider-type='percent'>0%</div>   
      </div>
    </div>
      <div class='description'>
        <p><strong>Within the urban population, how are your cities laid out?</strong></p>
        <p>The richer your population, the more resources you have to allocate to cater to their needs!</p>
      </div>
    <div data-choice-type='slidergroup'>
      <div>Rich, Suburbs
        <div class='slider' data-slider-name='d_hou_sub' data-slider-options='{"range":"min","value":25,"step":25,"animate":"true"}'>
          <div data-max-limit=25 class='max-limit l75'></div>
          <div class='step s0'><div class='name'>0%</div></div>
          <div class='step s25'><div class='name'>25%</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class='slidervalue hidden' data-slider-type='percent'>0%</div> 
      </div>
      <div>Middle-class, Appartments
        <div class='slider' data-slider-name='d_hou_apa' data-slider-options='{"range":"min","value":50,"step":25,"animate":"true"}'>
          <div data-min-limit=25 class='min-limit l25'></div>
          <div data-max-limit=75 class='max-limit l25'></div>
          <div class='step s25'><div class='name'>25%</div></div>
          <div class='step s50'><div class='name'>50%</div></div>
          <div class='step s75'><div class='name'>75%</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class='slidervalue hidden' data-slider-type='percent'>0%</div> 
      </div>
      <div>Poor, Slums
        <div class='slider' data-slider-name='d_hou_slu' data-slider-options='{"range":"min","value":25,"step":25,"animate":"true"}'>
          <div data-max-limit=50 class='max-limit l50'></div>
          <div class='step s0'><div class='name'>0%</div></div>
          <div class='step s25'><div class='name'>25%</div></div>
          <div class='step s50'><div class='name'>50%</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class='slidervalue hidden' data-slider-type='percent'>0%</div> 
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='text-center'>
      <a href='#services' class='nav-link'><div class='btn btn-primary btn-lg'>Next</div></a>
    </div>
  </div>
